          <text><![CDATA[<p><b> PACT (Protecting All College Tuition) Act of 2015</b></p> <p>This bill amends the federal bankruptcy code, with respect to transfers of interests that may be avoided by a bankruptcy trustee, to except tuition payments by a parent to an institution of higher education for the education of that parent's child. </p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2015-05-12T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
        </item>
