    <title>PACT (Protecting All College Tuition) Act of 2015</title>
    <titles>
      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <parentTitleType />
        <title>To amend title 11, United States Code, to provide an exception to the avoidance of transactions by bankruptcy trustee under section 548 where the transaction was a good faith payment by a parent of post secondary education tuition for that parent's child.</title>
